Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはづに さくやこのはな ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花開難波津 寒冬閉羞顏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的你看了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了 看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生裡有模特兒綾瀨千歲的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 我可是她的粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思很可愛囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾班的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每天午休的時候她都在大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨千早 競技歌牌部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那皮帶什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學 你怎麼又那副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 是老師說裙子不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿的話就只穿運動裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個宣傳海報只能貼一張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這種地方脫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說起來 根據那個傳聞說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得那麼漂亮 但是一動一說就全報廢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無用美人來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,80)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK}第一首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,240)\fn@MHGHagoromoTHK-Medium\frz270\fad(100,300)}花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒人來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 不要玩什麼歌牌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起搞田徑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短距離跑進了市區大賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人才浪費了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}註釋： 出現在江戶版的古典伊呂波歌牌中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌是那個「禍福皆因強出頭」？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言田徑部屬於邂逅型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅型？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊吶 快去社部活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然前輩又要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見了 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說那個前輩啊 好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 有伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想著在高中找到伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身心投入歌牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 綾瀨同學就是女王啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}たれをかも しるひとにせむ たかさごの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}訪舊皆難見 可憐無故知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌真正有趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你擺著大文字形睡在這
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才被人叫做無用美人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}まつもむかしの ともならなくに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}高砂松樹在 自小不相識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一竟然和我同一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你直升進了名校的高中部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在單程花一個半小時的地方 誰還能再去三年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說好疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過千早考進都立的好高中才意外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒差多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會長高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貌似也能長高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 太一 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你不受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？在車站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 在分倍河原等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一有女朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 打擊到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只是被告白就交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼喜歡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道新也找到了比歌牌更重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新有連絡過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也沒來賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似也沒有參加去年的全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中學的時候是田徑部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江神宮的全國大賽一次都沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田徑部不是挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高中也準備幹點別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌始終只是興趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一不玩歌牌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得在一個高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學我也主要在足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能一直都玩歌牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たれをかも しるひとにせむ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訪舊皆難見 可憐無故知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是舊友不在的和歌來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下去就還能再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 東京
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不知何為熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶 你姐姐的美少女選美怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然留到最終選拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明天報紙上會登姐姐照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的姐姐很漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一也這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和千早不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 只有運動神經能和我相比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有身高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 想打架嗎 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個轉校生 都不說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似也沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說還是別和那傢伙沾邊比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那傢伙點心吃蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班的傢伙看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襪子有洞洞眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班才不需要他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把綿谷同學的福井話都記錄下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近都不肯和我們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加不了啦 小氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是綿谷同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會和要嘲笑自己而記錄的人說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我說你把路程表忘記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住了？ 今天才是第一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有二百家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二丁目五區 藤原家加對面五家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大澤 藤宮 山本 內山家停止投遞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫田公寓 101 103
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,203 204
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐 上報了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 照片也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留到最後十五個人也很厲害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把這照片留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是的確是這個獲獎的女生身材好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立馬把想的都說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千我看了報紙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 好厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的登啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說雖然是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早卻還像個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回坐位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們 小倉百人一首和歌選貼紙集滿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住一百首的話 就過來我這裡測試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}能記住的人 就請參加下個月的歌牌大賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你記住多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道學習比不上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島 完美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他無所不能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不單單只有真島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個班級裡還有一個人完全記住了一百首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放學之後 綿谷同學來我這裡接受測試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣全背出來了一百首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給予他掌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}真的一口氣背完?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會參加下個月的歌牌大會吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報童！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 綿谷早上來發報紙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報童？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生不能兼職的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…綿谷同學真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被人拜託的時候才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道家裡貧困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那傢伙 好像每天都穿同條褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷他厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報童喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也要努力記住一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 真島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 弄髒你的獨件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天沒衣服穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你媽媽的裙子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到你會做出這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你為什麼老幫他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天大家都不理千早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會這樣做的 說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後你哭也不關我事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真殘舊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這人總是把想到話的直接說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以早上被姐姐踹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 你可以說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做記錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼早上你特意等報紙呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她參加選美大賽 所以想快點看到那個報導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是希望姐姐能成為日本第一的模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的不叫夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己的事就不叫夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能強加到別人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 那綿谷你有什麼夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 什麼 這不是百人一首和歌牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨你會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說我們學校每年都會舉行歌牌大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老師不是說過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但沒有讀牌的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錄音帶 錄音帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的幹勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 是怎樣來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把25張牌排成3行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀出上句後 取寫著下句的歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只記住了五十首…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 破歌牌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あらしふく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯颯飄紅葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たつたのかはの にしきなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清波成錦繡 斑斕龍田川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又插上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ながらへば またこのごろや しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}若得人長在 今朝亦留痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}よのなかよ みちこそなけれ おもひいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}哀哀人世路 隱遁嘆無歸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌是這樣子的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少得取上一張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認得這張牌的上句
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}せをはやみ いはにせかるる たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急流岩上碎 無奈兩離分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少那張也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一張也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}…をはやみ いはにせかるる たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…流岩上碎 無奈兩離分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}われてもすゑに …
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}早晚終相會 …
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了 從綿谷手上拿到一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 你太強悍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 綾瀨不也拿到一張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一張而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在福井 經常和大家都玩歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 來到東京之後就不怎麼玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我自己一個人在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人? 聽著錄音帶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌在外國還不怎麼流行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難也是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本取得第一名的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是世界第一了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第一?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是當上歌牌名人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早」真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 綾瀨的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(520,440)}悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張牌的上句就是以「千早振留」開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是按「千早」所取的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能看到「千早」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛是這樣看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 有朋友來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 難道是女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女朋友 要吃芋頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる かみよもきかず たつたがは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠神代事 黯黯不曾聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他搶牌真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}からくれなゐに みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓染龍田川 潺潺流水深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和新玩歌牌的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解到的不是歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是新的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:51.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:57.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:02.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:11.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:18.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:24.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:30.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:39.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:51.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:57.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:02.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:11.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:18.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:24.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:30.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在的話似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}試著伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:39.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在夢想的路上終有一天會再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.04,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行くあてない街
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:34.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり先を歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:39.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕日に照らされた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:44.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失いそうな心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わってゆくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:54.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想いもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:59.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:04.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつの間に違う方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:08.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歩いてたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:13.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしていま　ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:18.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠すぎる世界見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:24.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしていま　ほら　響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:31.68,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が教えてくれた歌　この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.04,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向著無名的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:34.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}形單影隻地前進著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:39.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被夕陽照得通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:44.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}近乎要遺失的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻逐漸發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:54.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我萬萬也沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:59.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與你在一起的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:04.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不覺之間我們卻已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:08.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走向了不同的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:13.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:18.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望著遙不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:24.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是此刻 你瞧 歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:31.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠 迴響於這片天空
